Description: GTK3 frontend for mpv media player
 mate-mpv is the spiritual successor to GNOME-Mplayer, providing a
 simple and clean GTK3 interface for the mpv media player. It supports
 audio and video playback with subtitle and audio track selection,
 persistent language preferences, and full-screen mode.
